caption: b'If you have diabetes, make sure to give extra love and attention to your eyes, hands and feet. Diabetes can cause a lack of feeling in your extremities\xe2\x80\x94turning minor problems like cuts into more serious issues like foot ulcers. On top of that, high blood sugar can damage the sensitive blood vessels around the eyes and lead to serious eye conditions such as diabetic retinopathy, macular edema, glaucoma and cataracts. Take your health into your hands by seeing your doctor regularly and establishing a routine that keeps every part of you healthy and happy. #DiabetesAwarenessMonth'
